According to the ''Declaration of Model Names'' document submitted to the FCC, :the following models are all identical with two of them classed as AC2400 :(256QAM disabled) and the other two as AC2600: *AC2400 (600Mbps, 2.4GHz 802.11n): [[ASUS RT-AC85P]], [[ASUS RT-AC2400]] *AC2600 (800Mbps, 2.4GHz 802.11n): [[ASUS RT-AC2600]], [[ASUS RT-ACRH26]]
